sentences: This dictionary aims to describe all the vocabulary items of the twenty Tinellbian languages consisting of High Lulani and its descendants
In addition miscellaneous English neologisms have been added including proper nouns
The search box at the bottom of each page allows one to proceed directly to any dictionary entry
Contrariwise the search box in the navigation pane runs a general search of the site
